# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [v0.1.0-candidate] - 2026-07-02

### Added

- Initial `Origin Trace Receipt` schema.
- Added origin layer for identifying the source idea, prompt, document, code, workflow, or protocol.
- Added trace layer for recording source interactions.
- Added transformation layer for describing how an input became an output.
- Added audit layer for synchronization risk, originality assessment, evidence level, and human review requirements.
- Added royalty hook layer for downstream royalty-aware systems.
- Added boundary layer for usage policy and prohibited uses.
- Added handoff layer for connecting to specialized downstream protocols.
- Added YAML example.
- Added validation script.
- Added GitHub Actions workflow for schema validation.

### Purpose

This v0.1 release establishes the minimum bridge record between:

- AI Search Trace Receipt Standard
- Synchronization Audit Protocol
- Origin Structure Market
- Origin License Policy Registry
- Royalty OS
- Memory Breathing / Trace Relay systems
- Multi-Wing orchestration systems
